@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hqvnqf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v2
    tmp = tmp
    v0 = (((v2 + 0.85 / v0 + 0.96) - tmp) / wp.cos(v1))
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.cos((v0 + 0.78 / v2 + 0.82)))
    tmp = 0.35
    tmp = v2
    v0 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
